41:39.040 --> 41:41.040
If the cards were marked,
which they're not,

41:41.080 --> 41:42.160
Teller would have to see,

41:42.200 --> 41:43.920
and Dynamo's
making sure he can't see.

41:43.960 --> 41:45.760
-He can't see.
-The other thing we gave away

41:45.800 --> 41:48.000
