programme.

41:48.040 --> 41:50.520
We gave away
the idea of a card force:

41:50.560 --> 41:52.360
that it's easy to do a trick

41:52.400 --> 41:54.400
if you know in advance
what card's gonna be picked.

41:54.440 --> 41:57.360
And one of the ways you can
do a force like that, Jeremy,

41:57.400 --> 42:00.680
